This is to inform the general public that application for online ‘Associate’ membership programme course of the Association of Investment Advisers and Portfolio Managers (IAPM) has commenced. Those who are interested to become Associate of IAPM are invited to apply. OBJECTIVE OF PROGRAMME The objective of the programme is to provide a structured and qualitative, world class programme in Investment Management and Financial Advisory to individuals who are interested to be qualified as Professional Investment Advisers and Portfolio Managers. BENEFITS FOR MEMBERS Qualified candidate will benefit from the following: ADMISSION REQUIREMENTS COURSE DURATION Three months intensive lectures before qualifying examination Closing Date: 27th May, 2022 Lecture’s Commence: 28th May, 2022 Registration Link: http://www.aiapm.org/Associate-Conversion-Programme-Application Application Method: Application forms are available at the Associations’ Secretariat, Reinsurance Building (10th Floor), 46, Marina, Lagos or register online through IAPM website: www.aiapm.org . Submit your application form with a fee of N10,000 cheque or bank draft made payable to the Association of Investment Advisers and Portfolio Managers or pay to the Association’s account No. 0002838280 in any branch of Union Bank of Nigeria Plc., nationwide and attach the evidence of payment. For further enquiries contact: IAPM Secretariat 46, Marina, Reinsurance Building, Lagos (10th Floor) Call: 08098450505, 08035292833, 08033350505 Email:  info@aiapm.org Twitter: @iapm_NG